data.description: Tranquil 25-Acre Haven with Creeks and Paved Road Access in Enchanting Ellijay, Georgia Welcome to your slice of paradise nestled in the heart of Ellijay, Georgia! This remarkable 25-acre property offers an idyllic blend of natural beauty and modern convenience, making it the perfect canvas for your dream retreat. With serene creeks, paved road access, and an abundance of prime building locations, this exceptional land promises a lifestyle of unparalleled tranquility and possibilities Picturesque Acreage: Embrace the allure of 25 sprawling acres, adorned with towering trees, vibrant wildflowers, and an aura of peace that only nature can provide.Creek Charms: The property boasts a meandering creek that add an enchanting touch to the landscape. The gentle babbling sounds and crystal-clear waters provide an oasis of relaxation and a picturesque backdrop for your future haven.Easy Access: Paved road access ensures a seamless journey to and from your new retreat. Enjoy the harmony of rural living while maintaining proximity to the amenities and conveniences of Ellijay's charming downtown. Endless Building Potential: Choose your own adventure with numerous optimal building spots spread throughout the property. Craft your custom-designed residence, create a family compound, or construct the ultimate weekend getawayGthe canvas is yours. Seize the chance to turn your vision of rural luxury into reality. With 25 acres of land, creek that soothe the soul, much more!
